  All Progressive Congress(APC) governorship aspirant in Edo, Pastor Osagie Ize-Iyamu has extolled the virtues of National Chairman of the (APC), Comrade Adams Oshiomhole, who clocked 68. In a birthday message he personally signed, Ize-Iyamu said: “Dear Comrade, you have remained steadfast over the years, even in the midst of raging storms and vicissitudes, and at 68, to our lasting admiration and respect, the pendulum is in no way tilting otherwise. “Our prayers for you on the occasion of your 68th birthday is that the Lord Almighty will grant you the grace of many more years in great health, limitless joy and vigor as you continue to apply yourself and wisdom in service to humanity and fatherland. “Happy Birthday, Comrade! I wish you many happy returns!”